OL,3,CMore than 250 patients a week 'die
OL,4,Cneedlessly due to long A&E waits'
OL,6,FIn February, the number of people
OL,7,Fwaiting more than 12 hours in A&E
OL,8,Fdepartments from a decision to admit
OL,9,Fto actually being admitted stood at
OL,10,F44,417.
OL,12,FFor its new excess death estimates,
OL,13,Fthe RCEM used a very large study of
OL,14,Fmore than five million NHS patients
OL,15,Fpublished in the Emergency Medicine
OL,16,FJournal (EMJ) in 2021.
OL,18,FThis found there was one excess death
OL,19,Ffor every 72 patients that spent eight
OL,20,Fto 12 hours in an A&E department.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/13
