OL,6,FDr Adrian Boyle, president of the
OL,7,FRCEM, said: "Excessively long waits
OL,8,Fcontinue to put patients at risk of
OL,9,Fserious harm.
OL,11,F"Small improvements in four-hour
OL,12,Faccess standard performance are not
OL,13,Fmeaningful when there are so many
OL,14,Fpeople staying more than 12 hours.
OL,15,FEffort and money should go where the
OL,16,Fharm is greatest.
OL,18,F"In 2023, more than 1.5 million
OL,19,Fpatients waited 12 hours or more in
OL,20,Fmajor emergency departments, with 65%
OL,21,Fof those awaiting admission.
