OL,6,F"Lack of hospital capacity means that
OL,7,Fpatients are staying in longer than
OL,8,Fnecessary and continue to be cared for
OL,9,Fby emergency department staff, often
OL,10,Fin clinically inappropriate areas such
OL,11,Fas corridors or ambulances.
OL,13,F"The direct correlation between delays
OL,14,Fand mortality rates is clear. Patients
OL,15,Fare being subjected to avoidable harm.
